headline: Ball (BALL): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q1 Earnings?
summary: Ball trades at $58.01 per share and has stayed right on track with the overall market, gaining 6.8% over the last six months. At the same time, the S&P 500 has returned 3.7%.
